Entry.JapaneseText: クレアさん、ひさしぶりの スールズはどうだった？
Entry.EnglishText: So Claire, how'd you like Sulz after being gone for so long?

Entry.JapaneseText: え？ え？ わ、わたくしは……
この前の旅で、あちこち行ったけど、 やっぱり、生まれ育ったところが一番だよな！
Entry.EnglishText: I traveled to many places on my last journey, but there's nothing better than the place you were born and raised!

Entry.JapaneseText: え、ええ……そ、そうですわね…… やはり生まれ育ったところが……
Entry.EnglishText: Y-Yes... I concur... The place you were born and raised...
